    • getResultsForId

      public static Map<String,String> getResultsForId(@NonNull @NonNull String submissionId) throws IllegalArgumentException
      Returns the results map for the Results object associated with the given submission id, if one exists.
      Parameters:
      submissionId - The submission id of the project, cannot be null
      Returns:
      A map containing all the data of a results object associated with the provided id, or an empty map if no such object exists
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the provided submission id is empty
